        <p>File expenses on {{config.host.website}}/{{collective.slug}}/expenses/new and don't forget to approve them (any admin of the collective –aka core contributor– can approve or reject expenses). Your host organization (the <a href="https://opencollective.com/opensource">Open Source Collective 501c6</a>) pays out once a week all the expenses that have been approuved.</p>
